text: Yadanar Khin () is a Burmese film actress and model, most popular in the 2000s. She attended the Practising School Yangon Institute of Education. She married her husband, Soe Hlaing U, in 2005, with whom she has three sons, Zwe U Htet, Htun Myat U, and Kaung Hset U. She is currently a restaurateur, with several Burmese-style restaurants in Yangon. ==Filmography== ===Films=== ==References== Category:Living people Category:1980 births Category:Burmese film actresses Category:People from Yangon
